# wallet/ — self-managed BSV HD wallet environment template
#
# Copy this file to `wallet/.env` and fill in values for your machine.
# NEVER commit a real `.env`. The wallet's root secret (master mnemonic) and all
# derived WIF keys live OUTSIDE the repo under $BONSAI_NOTARY_HOME/wallet — not here.
# This template holds non-secret config only.

# Optional WhatsOnChain API key for read queries + broadcast against
# https://api.whatsonchain.com/v1/bsv/main. Leave blank to use the unauthenticated
# rate-limited tier; set a key to raise rate limits.
WHATSONCHAIN_API_KEY=
